General.Name: Cazaly Resources Ltd
General.Description: Cazaly Resources Limited operates as a diversified mineral exploration and resource development company in Australia. The company primarily explores for nickel, graphite, gold, copper, iron ore, and cobalt deposits. It holds interests in the Halls Creek Copper, Ashburton, Vanrock polymetallic, Yabby, Kaoko Kobalt, McKenzie Springs, and Mount Venn projects. The company was incorporated in 2002 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
